---
// About section component
---

<section id="about" class="about">
	<div class="about-bg-particles">
		<div class="particle-about"></div>
		<div class="particle-about"></div>
		<div class="particle-about"></div>
		<div class="particle-about"></div>
		<div class="particle-about"></div>
		<div class="particle-about"></div>
	</div>
	<div class="container">
		<h2 class="about-title">Sobre Mí</h2>
		<div class="about-content">
			<div class="about-text">
				<div class="text-highlight">
					<p>Soy estudiante de cuarto año de Ingeniería en Sistemas de Información en la Universidad Tecnológica Nacional (UTN), donde obtuve mi título de Analista Desarrollador de Sistemas de Información. Me considero proactivo y resolutivo, con facilidad para aprender sobre la marcha y adaptarme a nuevos entornos tecnológicos.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="text-highlight">
					<p>Me interesa construir soluciones útiles, claras y bien pensadas que realmente aporten valor. Busco encontrar la mejor solución posible para cada problema, combinando criterio técnico con enfoque práctico. Trabajo de manera organizada y colaborativa, priorizando la calidad y la mantenibilidad del código.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="text-highlight">
					<p>Estoy comprometido con el aprendizaje continuo para mantenerme actualizado con las mejores prácticas del desarrollo. Creo que la tecnología debe resolver problemas reales de manera eficiente y accesible.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="about-visual">
				<div class="tech-pattern">
					<div class="pattern-element core"></div>
					<div class="pattern-element orbit-1"></div>
					<div class="pattern-element orbit-2"></div>
					<div class="pattern-element orbit-3"></div>
					<div class="pattern-element satellite"></div>
					<div class="connection-lines">
						<svg class="connections" viewBox="0 0 300 300" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
							<path d="M150 80 L120 120 L180 120 Z" stroke="rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.4)" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
							<path d="M150 220 L120 180 L180 180 Z" stroke="rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.4)" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
							<path d="M80 150 L120 120 L120 180 Z" stroke="rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.4)" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
							<path d="M220 150 L180 120 L180 180 Z" stroke="rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.4)" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.about {
		padding: 5rem 2rem;
		background:
			linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fffe 0%, #e8f5f0 50%, #f0fdf4 100%),
			radial-gradient(circle at 20% 80%, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%),
			radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%);
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	.about::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		bottom: 0;
		background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><defs><pattern id="leaves" width="30" height="30" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><path d="M15 8 Q20 3 25 8 Q20 13 15 8" fill="none" stroke="%2316a34a" stroke-width="0.3" opacity="0.08"/><circle cx="15" cy="8" r="1" fill="%234ade80" opacity="0.1"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100" height="100" fill="url(%23leaves)"/></svg>');
		pointer-events: none;
		animation: patternFloat 20s ease-in-out infinite;
	}
	@keyframes patternFloat {
		0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg); }
		50% { transform: translate(-10px, -5px) rotate(1deg); }
	}
	.about-bg-particles {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		pointer-events: none;
	}
	.particle-about {
		position: absolute;
		width: 3px;
		height: 3px;
		background: linear-gradient(45deg, #4ade80, #22c55e);
		border-radius: 50%;
		opacity: 0.4;
		animation: particleDrift 10s ease-in-out infinite;
	}
	.particle-about:nth-child(1) { top: 15%; left: 10%; animation-delay: 0s; }
	.particle-about:nth-child(2) { top: 25%; right: 20%; animation-delay: 3s; }
	.particle-about:nth-child(3) { bottom: 35%; left: 25%; animation-delay: 6s; }
	.particle-about:nth-child(4) { top: 70%; right: 15%; animation-delay: 9s; }
	.particle-about:nth-child(5) { bottom: 15%; right: 30%; animation-delay: 12s; }
	.particle-about:nth-child(6) { top: 45%; left: 70%; animation-delay: 15s; }
	@keyframes particleDrift {
		0%, 100% {
			transform: translateY(0px) translateX(0px) scale(1);
			opacity: 0.4;
		}
		50% {
			transform: translateY(-25px) translateX(20px) scale(1.3);
			opacity: 0.8;
		}
	}
	.container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
	}
	.about h2 {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		color: #0f5132;
		font-weight: 700;
		position: relative;
		animation: titleSlideIn 1s ease-out;
	}
	.about-title::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		bottom: -10px;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		width: 80px;
		height: 4px;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4ade80, #22c55e);
		border-radius: 2px;
		animation: lineExpand 1s ease-out 0.5s both;
	}
	@keyframes titleSlideIn {
		from {
			opacity: 0;
			transform: translateY(-30px);
		}
		to {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: translateY(0);
		}
	}
	@keyframes lineExpand {
		from { width: 0; }
		to { width: 80px; }
	}
	.about-content {
		display: flex;
		gap: 4rem;
		align-items: center;
		animation: contentFadeIn 1s ease-out 0.3s both;
	}
	@keyframes contentFadeIn {
		from { opacity: 0; }
		to { opacity: 1; }
	}
	.about-text {
		flex: 2;
	}
	.text-highlight {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		border-left: 4px solid #4ade80;
		border-radius: 0 15px 15px 0;
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		animation: highlightSlideIn 0.8s ease-out both;
	}
	.text-highlight:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
	.text-highlight:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.7s; }
	.text-highlight:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.9s; }
	.text-highlight:hover {
		transform: translateX(10px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2);
	}
	@keyframes highlightSlideIn {
		from {
			opacity: 0;
			transform: translateX(-50px);
		}
		to {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: translateX(0);
		}
	}
	.about-text p {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin: 0;
		color: #1f2937;
		font-weight: 400;
	}
	.about-visual {
		flex: 1;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		animation: visualSlideIn 1s ease-out 0.8s both;
	}
	@keyframes visualSlideIn {
		from {
			opacity: 0;
			transform: translateX(50px) scale(0.9);
		}
		to {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: translateX(0) scale(1);
		}
	}
	.tech-pattern {
		position: relative;
		width: 320px;
		height: 320px;
		animation: patternRotate 20s linear infinite;
	}
	@keyframes patternRotate {
		from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
		to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
	}
	.pattern-element {
		position: absolute;
		border-radius: 50%;
		transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
		cursor: pointer;
	}
	.pattern-element:hover {
		transform: scale(1.2);
		box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.6);
	}
	.pattern-element.core {
		width: 80px;
		height: 80px;
		background: linear-gradient(45deg, #16a34a, #22c55e);
		border: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		top: 50%;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
		box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.4);
		animation: corePulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
	}
	@keyframes corePulse {
		0%, 100% {
			box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.4);
			transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1);
		}
		50% {
			box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.7);
			transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.05);
		}
	}
	.pattern-element.orbit-1 {
		width: 50px;
		height: 50px;
		background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.8), rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.6));
		border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
		top: 20%;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		animation: orbit1 8s linear infinite;
	}
	@keyframes orbit1 {
		from { transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(0deg) translateY(-120px) rotate(0deg); }
		to { transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(360deg) translateY(-120px) rotate(-360deg); }
	}
	.pattern-element.orbit-2 {
		width: 40px;
		height: 40px;
		background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.7), rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.5));
		border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
		top: 50%;
		right: 15%;
		animation: orbit2 12s linear infinite reverse;
	}
	@keyframes orbit2 {
		from { transform: rotate(0deg) translateX(120px) rotate(0deg); }
		to { transform: rotate(360deg) translateX(120px) rotate(-360deg); }
	}
	.pattern-element.orbit-3 {
		width: 35px;
		height: 35px;
		background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.6), rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.4));
		border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
		bottom: 20%;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		animation: orbit3 10s linear infinite;
	}
	@keyframes orbit3 {
		from { transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(0deg) translateY(120px) rotate(0deg); }
		to { transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(360deg) translateY(120px) rotate(-360deg); }
	}
	.pattern-element.satellite {
		width: 25px;
		height: 25px;
		background: linear-gradient(45deg, #4ade80, #22c55e);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		top: 10%;
		right: 20%;
		animation: satelliteMove 15s ease-in-out infinite;
	}
	@keyframes satelliteMove {
		0%, 100% {
			transform: translateY(0px) translateX(0px) scale(1);
		}
		25% {
			transform: translateY(-20px) translateX(30px) scale(1.1);
		}
		50% {
			transform: translateY(10px) translateX(60px) scale(0.9);
		}
		75% {
			transform: translateY(-10px) translateX(30px) scale(1.05);
		}
	}
	.connection-lines {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		pointer-events: none;
	}
	.connections path {
		stroke-dasharray: 8, 8;
		animation: dashFlow 6s linear infinite;
	}
	@keyframes dashFlow {
		to { stroke-dashoffset: -16; }
	}
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.about {
			padding: 3rem 1rem;
		}
		.about-content {
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 2rem;
		}
		.about h2 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}
		.about-title::after {
			width: 60px;
		}
		.about-text p {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}
		.text-highlight {
			padding: 1rem;
			margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		}
		.text-highlight:hover {
			transform: translateX(5px);
		}
		.tech-pattern {
			width: 250px;
			height: 250px;
		}
		.pattern-element.core {
			width: 60px;
			height: 60px;
		}
		.pattern-element.orbit-1 {
			width: 40px;
			height: 40px;
		}
		.pattern-element.orbit-2 {
			width: 35px;
			height: 35px;
		}
		.pattern-element.orbit-3 {
			width: 30px;
			height: 30px;
		}
		.pattern-element.satellite {
			width: 20px;
			height: 20px;
		}
		.about-bg-particles .particle-about {
			width: 2px;
			height: 2px;
		}
	}
</style>
<!-- About.astro -->